      • NPY_1_7_API_VERSION

        public static final int NPY_1_7_API_VERSION
        To help with the NPY_NO_DEPRECATED_API macro, we include API version numbers for specific versions of NumPy. To exclude all API that was deprecated as of 1.7, add the following before #including any NumPy headers: #define NPY_NO_DEPRECATED_API NPY_1_7_API_VERSION
